graph TD
    A[Event Loop Tick] --> B[Select Macrotask]
    B --> C[Execute Macrotask]
    C --> D[Call Stack Empty?]
    D -->|No| C
    D -->|Yes| E[Microtask Checkpoint]
    E --> F[Process All Microtasks]
    F --> G[Microtask Queue Empty?]
    G -->|No| F
    G -->|Yes| H[Next Phase]
    H --> A
